name: Ag Processing RBD-High Oleic Soybean Salad Oil
description: Ag Processing RBD-High Oleic Soybean Salad Oil is refined at our refinery in Hastings, Nebraska, to meet the growing demand for high oleic oil. It is 100% fully refined, bleached, and deodorized high oleic soybean. Careful bleaching assures oil with light color making it the oil of choice when bottled for foodservice or retail distribution. Thorough refining and deodorization guarantee that the oil will not mask the natural flavor profile of your food products. High oleic soybean oil maintains excellent stability and its unique fatty acid profile makes it healthy 0g trans fat choice when a liquid vegetable oil is preferred.
